column3: i see that you have           finally arrived huh?
you will now face                          something that you will               hardly forget.
i have told you from                  many genocide routes                before...
but you didn't listen to          me.
you could have fixed             all this in only a press      of a button.
you could made your                decision and finally have            a good ending.
now you will face out            your consequences...
